articles.title: Andy Maloney wins Finn Gold Cup - Stuff.co.nz
articles.description: America's Cup winner holds on for world title in Portugal, now waits to see if it earns him Olympic selection.
articles.content:
New Zealand sailor Andy Maloney has hung on to win the Finn Gold Cup and now waits to see if it will clinch him selection for the Tokyo Olympics.
